    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "The lists here are remarkably different from those in marginal references Probably the persons here mentioned were not literally \"sons,\" but were among the later descendants of the founders, being the chief men of the family at the time of David's census. ",
